{"tid":2060100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來今年啲蝗蟲分分鐘仲帶有毒素","createTime":"2020-06-11T11:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T14:53:17.000Z","uid":58841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"38dbc95071321f3aab45a971fb9c1bc7a28bc1cc","tid":2060100,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"4.然而從去年開始，草地貪夜蛾在中國境內落地生根，一旦爆發大規模的蟲害就很可能縮減本土蝗蟲的棲地<br />\n<br />\n如果不曉得草地貪夜蛾是什麼東西的蔥友，可以參考一下維基（草地貪夜蛾）。<br />\n至於說為什麼會縮減本土蝗蟲的棲地，<span style=\"color: red;\">那是因為這玩意比蝗蟲還能吃，而且習性比蝗蟲更麻煩</span>，因為這些特點，他們數量成長時就會自然壓縮蝗蟲的棲地（不是好事，是爛到不行的壞事）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.當蝗蟲從孤生相轉變為群生相(綠色到枯黃色)時，那就是蝗災的起點<br />\n<br />\n簡單來說就是蝗蟲在成長過程中，因為食物不足且數量密度太高，會逐漸從非群聚型突變成群聚型蝗蟲，改變地方大致是：<br />\n翅膀變得更強壯、蟲肢更有力、體表顏色改變。<br />\n這些都是讓蝗蟲能夠長距離遷徙的突變，換句話說就是蝗災開始爆發，而且群聚型蝗蟲的後代一出生就是群聚型，等於越吃越多。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外，顏色改變除了威嚇還有一個作用，那就是帶有毒素，所以別相信甚麼雞鴨大軍滅蝗蟲的故事，別被毒死就不錯了。</span><br />\n<br />\n非洲個堆仲未黎本土個啲已經進化緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCLS<br />\n其實蝗災未爆架 而家只係開始"},{"pid":"dc7509230f52493f375083b74eec4dab74c820d7","tid":2060100,"uid":189523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:26:46.000Z","msg":"草娥頂住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94982f9e34f94fd83ca90a432af3af451932c905","tid":2060100,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:27:04.000Z","msg":"你當支那人死架？佢地連屎都食，點會怕毒"},{"pid":"158440f3eeb7eca8833852b7dca54307ecbc22ac","tid":2060100,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:27:13.000Z","msg":"集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd882f3db900502c291634092acbe470d113eb8a","tid":2060100,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:27:40.000Z","msg":"南方只係落個雨就周圍水浸冧樓<br />\n如果到7月蝗蟲同颱風打孖上點撚搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813a225671612d9d9f4090e9029bb6739b389e11","tid":2060100,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:27:41.000Z","msg":"以為你講緊開關之後啲支那畜仲係帶菌"},{"pid":"3f7398f3d081e9f6b5b0c258a2d80a0de09d456a","tid":2060100,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"813a225671612d9d9f4090e9029bb6739b389e11","tid":2060100,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:27:41.000Z","msg":"以為你講緊開關之後啲支那畜仲係帶菌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:28:53.000Z","msg":"一定帶 唔洗以為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e873687f11c7b60cdba04247a19aa3b71f9151","tid":2060100,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd882f3db900502c291634092acbe470d113eb8a","tid":2060100,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:27:40.000Z","msg":"南方只係落個雨就周圍水浸冧樓<br />\n如果到7月蝗蟲同颱風打孖上點撚搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"加埋地震 好快到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f608235ff12d4e967d76f0ade35dff39ce6d8744","tid":2060100,"uid":149524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:31:07.000Z","msg":"毒？支那人驚系咩<br />\n支那好多嘢食都有毒架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795a3e775e7adb5bd2baaca7f23bfee94e10067a","tid":2060100,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:32:12.000Z","msg":"如果有人係中国放蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6962ff399c594266e